(1, 'Building A Simple Web App Using CodeIgniter 4 - Part 1 | Starter Pack', 'http://localhost:8080/public/uploads/1702814790_ab596453af58e0e6d836.png', '<p id=\"4452\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">In Part 1 of this blog, we will be building a Simple Blog using <a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">CodeIgniter&nbsp;</a>4. This mini project would be ideal for many&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">CodeIgniter</a>&nbsp;newbies.</p>\r\n<p id=\"d2e7\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Through my days of Web Development I have come across many Technologies, Libraries, Frameworks etc. to build Web Applications.</p>\r\n<p id=\"4059\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">My focus on this blog is&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">CodeIgniter</a> 4, which is one of my personal favourites and a very famous MVC Framework among Web Developers for building commercial Web Applications.</p>\r\n<p id=\"2655\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">I&rsquo;m really excited to working with&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">CodeIgniter</a>&nbsp;4 and amazed by how much the contributors have been able to accomplish by rewiring/rewriting&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">CodeIgniter</a>&nbsp;3 code base.</p>\r\n<h1 id=\"5aac\" class=\"nw nx gr be ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq or os ot bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">What are the requirements to run CodeIgniter 4?</h1>\r\n<figure class=\"ox oy oz pa pb pc ou ov paragraph-image\">\r\n<div class=\"pd pe fg pf bg pg\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\">\r\n<div class=\"ou ov ow\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 1400w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png 1400w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" data-testid=\"og\"><img class=\"bg me ph c\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1050/1*cGtJasESNZ3BIBx75V-F0A.png\" alt=\"CodeIgniter 4 Server Requirements to run on the local PC\" width=\"700\" height=\"376\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"pi fc pj ou ov pk pl be b bf z dt\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/user_guide/intro/requirements.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">https://codeigniter.com/user_guide/intro/requirements.html</a></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p id=\"8b5c\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.php.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">PHP</a>&nbsp;Version 7.2 or newer is required. Having this in mind, let\'s Set up the Environment to run a <a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.php.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">PHP</a> code base. For this purpose, we will be using&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.apachefriends.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">XMPP</a>.</p>\r\n<blockquote class=\"pm pn po\">\r\n<p id=\"a13f\" class=\"mx my pp mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.apachefriends.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">XAMPP</a>&nbsp;is the most popular&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.php.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">PHP</a>&nbsp;development environment.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<figure class=\"ox oy oz pa pb pc ou ov paragraph-image\">\r\n<div class=\"pd pe fg pf bg pg\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\">\r\n<div class=\"ou ov ow\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 1400w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png 1400w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" data-testid=\"og\"><img class=\"bg me ph c\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1050/1*eneEciUcqtFEtlikBmHaBg.png\" alt=\"How to install XAMPP on the local PC\" width=\"700\" height=\"376\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"pi fc pj ou ov pk pl be b bf z dt\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.apachefriends.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">https://www.apachefriends.org/index.html</a></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h1 id=\"1719\" class=\"nw nx gr be ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq or os ot bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Starting the XMPP required services</h1>\r\n<p id=\"7e6e\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na pq nc nd ne pr ng nh ni ps nk nl nm pt no np nq pu ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Start Apache and&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.mysql.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">MySQL</a>&nbsp;services where we will be using them later on. Apache is the server that acts as the hosting where our source code will be kept. MySQL will be the type of database we will be using and to be connected to Models with relevance to the MVC Architecture.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"ox oy oz pa pb pc ou ov paragraph-image