ixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*DjMMUKKidCl7mNe175KgOQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*DjMMUKKidCl7mNe175KgOQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*DjMMUKKidCl7mNe175KgOQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*DjMMUKKidCl7mNe175KgOQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*DjMMUKKidCl7mNe175KgOQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*DjMMUKKidCl7mNe175KgOQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*DjMMUKKidCl7mNe175KgOQ.png 1400w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" data-testid=\"og\"><img class=\"bg me ph c\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1050/1*DjMMUKKidCl7mNe175KgOQ.png\" alt=\"XAMPP with the required services started\" width=\"700\" height=\"455\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"pi fc pj ou ov pk pl be b bf z dt\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">XAMPP with the required services started</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h1 id=\"d834\" class=\"nw nx gr be ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq or os ot bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Creating project directory</h1>\r\n<p id=\"4b59\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na pq nc nd ne pr ng nh ni ps nk nl nm pt no np nq pu ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Ones&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.apachefriends.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">XAMPP</a> required services are up and running, navigate to the directory C:\\xampp\\htdocs and create a New Folder with a name of your choice. In my case, it is ci-4-simple-blog.</p>\r\n<p id=\"9f05\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Navigate to the directory C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\ci-4-simple-blog. By now, we should be having something like this.</p>\r\n<p id=\"44b9\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><strong class=\"mz gs\"><em class=\"pp\">Ignore the .git folder,</em></strong><em class=\"pp\"> as I\'m using it for the purpose of version controlling the source code using Git.</em></p>\r\n<figure class=\"ox oy oz pa pb pc ou ov paragraph-image\">\r\n<div class=\"pd pe fg pf bg pg\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\">\r\n<div class=\"ou ov pw\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 1400w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png 1400w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" data-testid=\"og\"><img class=\"bg me ph c\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1050/1*73Ox_EQucUmew6dzfTE0qQ.png\" alt=\"Creating a new directory in XAMPP\" width=\"700\" height=\"466\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"pi fc pj ou ov pk pl be b bf z dt\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Creating a new directory in XAMPP</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p id=\"9209\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">When the project directory is created, it should be accessible via any browser and as long as the&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.apachefriends.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">XAMPP</a>&nbsp;required services are up and running.</p>\r\n<p id=\"9ff3\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><a class=\"af nv\" href=\"http://localhost%3cPORT%3e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">http://localhost:&lt;PORT&gt;/&lt;PROJECT_NAME&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p id=\"895e\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">In my case I have used the port :8012 since the default port :8080 is occupied. Therefore, <a class=\"af nv\" href=\"http://localhost/%3cPROJECT_NAME%3e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">http://localhost/&lt;PROJECT_NAME&gt;</a>&nbsp;should work for most of the users who have not adjusted default ports that the&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.apachefriends.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">XAMPP</a>&nbsp;is configured with.</p>\r\n<p id=\"44a3\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Therefore, I can access it via&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"http://localhost:8012/ci-4-simple-blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">http://localhost:8012/ci-4-simple-blog</a></p>\r\n<figure class=\"ox oy oz pa pb pc ou ov paragraph-image\">\r\n<div class=\"pd pe fg pf bg pg\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\">\r\n<div class=\"ou ov px\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 1400w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png 1400w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" data-testid=\"og\"><img class=\"bg me ph c\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1050/1*xwURrhAB4FXx9HQq1956nQ.png\" alt=\"Accessing the project URL via a browser\" width=\"700\" height=\"249\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"pi fc pj ou ov pk pl be b bf z dt\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Accessing the project URL via a browser</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h1 id=\"545b\" class=\"nw nx gr be ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq or os ot bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Installing the CodeIgniter 4 Framework Source Code</h1>\r\n<p id=\"6c78\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na pq nc nd ne pr ng nh ni ps nk nl nm pt no np nq pu ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Now that we have&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://www.apachefriends.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">XAMPP</a>&nbsp;Services Running, the Project Folder Created and it being Accessible Via the Browser, we can go ahead with downloading the&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">CodeIgniter</a>&nbsp;4 Framework source code and placing it in the project folder that we created which is C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\ci-4-simple-blog.</p>\r\n<p id=\"d77b\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mx my gr mz b na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu gk bj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">We can start by downloading the source code from the&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">CodeIgniter</a>&nbsp;Official website. Visit&nbsp;<a class=\"af nv\" href=\"https://codeigniter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\">CodeIgniter</a>&nbsp;Installation.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"ox oy oz pa pb pc ou ov paragraph-image\">\r\n<div class=\"pd pe fg pf bg pg\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\">\r\n<div class=\"ou ov ow\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*9Vg-8cgjzOVLPH7YRzd3jA.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*9Vg-8cgjzOVLPH7YRzd3jA.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*9Vg-8cgjzOVLPH7YRzd3jA.png 750w, https://m